{"tid":1579795,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫個忙！唔好再叫錯「急救員」做「救護員」","createTime":"2019-09-18T17:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T19:15:49.000Z","uid":306782,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd9f3d22d9bf0e3c81c1f57ac26ac394f779695","tid":1579795,"uid":306782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"夢遊期間，好多義務<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span></span></strong>出左黎照顧傷者，記住佢地係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span></span></strong>，唔係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span></span></strong>，係兩樣野呢咖！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span></span></strong><strong>通常</strong>係指上左30個鐘AFA班/BFA班/StJ/Red Cross.etc. 果堆<br />\n<br />\n而香港通常講既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span></span></strong>係消防處果啲救護員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩者係好大分別咖，不論持有既證書/技能上，所以各位手足/記者大哥唔好再叫錯啦<br />\n<br />\n成日起夢境聽到有人叫左啲<span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span>做<span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span>搞到本身應該要call白車處理既case ，有人以為<span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span>到左，冇再call白車，結果其實到左果個只係<span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span><br />\n<br />\n又有睇新聞同直播聽到有Press叫錯<br />\n又有報導大條道理咁屈啲<span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span>扮<span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span><br />\n<br />\n所以拜託大家 唔好再叫錯<span style=\"color: red;\">急救員</span>做<span style=\"color: blue;\">救護員</span>啦，免得比位人地入，同堆發生誤會，阻礙救援。"},{"pid":"381a291076a868f79777e4b5e388845a0bb78d93","tid":1579795,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feb1858ae807cf936a3796af747aed12d989f9e","tid":1579795,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8sQjh3.jpg\" data-thum